Everybody dreams of experiencing that rush of adrenaline when you stand atop of a hillock and watch those trees swaying while the water flows down a beautiful stream. Prepare yourself for one such expedition by packing your belongings in the Wildcraft Daypack A4 20 L Backpack. This backpack can be used by both men and women.

Body

This backpack is made of 210D Nylon Ripstop and 420D Nylon Dobby which lend it robustness and durability. The dimensions given to this bag are 279.4 x 482.6 x 152.4 mm in dimension this backpack compact but can accommodate all your essentials with ease. Weighing 560 g this bag is lightweight and easy to carry around. With a 20 litre carrying capacity this Wildcraft Daypack A4 20 L Backpack can accommodate all your essentials such as clothes accessories and equipment without much trouble.

Features

Equipped with three compartments and two pockets this backpack allows you to segregate all your items in order of use. Keeping your load in place and preventing it from shifting around unnecessarily are the sternum straps of this backpack. Ensuring you are comfortable while moving around are the padded shoulder straps and back. Facilitating easy portability of this backpack is the reinforced haul loop which can be used when you don’t want to strap it on. Giving you visibility when it is dark is the reflector tape on this bag. To ensure that you don’t have to stop every time you want a drink of water this backpack has a hydration bladder compartment and straps for holding hydration bladder. As this Wildcraft Daypack A4 20 L Backpack is bar tacked on specialised machines it is resilient to common damages like tearing and ripping.

Overcome your gear glitches with the Wildcraft Gangotri Rucksack-65 L. This unisex and free size bag is the right pick for adventure activities like trekking mountaineering and hiking. Body

Sturdiness and durability have been lent to this Wildcraft Gangotri Rucksack-65 L by the 210D Nylon Ripstop material. Measuring 330.2 x 787.4 x 254 mm in dimension and weighing 2140 g this bag has a compact profile. In order to divide the weight of the load evenly between your hip and shoulders and also to alter the height this bag has shoulder weight and width adjusters along with a torso height adjuster. With a carrying capacity of 65 litres this bag can accommodate quite a lot of things thus you won’t regret missing out any of your essentials due to lack of space. You can make the most of the top loading facility of this bag by packing your things in order of their use.


Features

The Wildcraft Gangotri Rucksack-65 L manufactured with multiple facets is a boon for avid travellers and adventure devotees. Forget about lugging around extra baggage as this bag comes with a sleeping bag carrier on the hood and carry mat straps at the base so go ahead and enjoy a nice nap on your carry mat or snuggle into your sleeping bag. In order to make sure that you reach the required tools in a flick this bag has walking stick and ice axe loops. To keep your load in place this bag has compression straps at the top and bottom which prevent the load from shifting. The generously padded shoulders back and waist belt give you a comfortable experience of carrying the load. To comply with your trekking and mountaineering activities this bag has webbing on the waist belt where you can clip on the carabiners or any other small accessories.

Sail through the problem of carrying your soiled clothes and shoes as this bag has a collapsible and zippered compartment specially designed for this purpose and when unzipped this space acts as extra storage capacity. Giving some relief to your shoulders from the burden of the load are the attached waist straps of this Wildcraft bag which even out the weight and make your movement easier. The snow skirt keeps your belongings dry and clean by preventing snow from depositing onto this bag. Making this bag more portable is the reinforced haul loop which can be used instead of the shoulder straps especially when the load is minimal.


This Wildcraft Gangotri Rucksack-65 L has been designed to suit all weather conditions thus it has a zippered rain cover pocket at the base (with rain cover) which protects your belongings from getting drenched in the rain. The six pockets in this bag allow you to arrange things according to your own convenience. For quick access to items you can place them in the concealed zippered pocket on the hood and the frequently used items can be placed in the internal flat pocket. Your miscellaneous items can be placed in the zippered front pocket of this bag. The detachable hood is another add-on of this bag which facilitates easy packing and unpacking. Making extra storage for your essentials this bag has side balloon pockets where you can keep the small items. While you are busy in adventure activities your possessions are kept safe by the buckle and zipper closure of this Wildcraft bag. Bar tacked on specialised machines this bag promises to accompany you for all your adventures.

Make the most out of your escapades with the free size Wildcraft Eiger Rucksack-40 L. This unisex rucksack gives you that special comfort and freedom that you have always wanted while camping hiking and mountaineering.

Body

Manufactured from 210 D Nylon Ripstop this bag is prevents your bag from tearing and ripping. Measuring 381 x 558.8 x 203.2 in dimensions this bag is the perfect gift for an adventure buff.  Weighing 1160 g this backpack has a slender profile. The shoulder weight and width adjusters on the shoulder pads give your shoulders a break from the heavy load.

This Wildcraft rucksack with a carrying capacity of 40 L can accommodate all your essentials. To make sure you reach all your possessions without much trouble this bag has a front loading style. The aluminium stays reduce the burden from your shoulders and transfer it to your hips.

Features

This smart Wildcraft Eiger Rucksack-40 L is a blessing in disguise for all your expeditions. The detachable angular waist belt when strapped on shift the load of the bag onto your hip. To prevent the load from shifting while you are walking jumping or hiking this bag has compression straps. In addition to these features this bag has generously padded shoulders back and waist belt. For equipment you need to grab during snowfall or any other situation this bag is equipped with walking stick and ice axe loops. You can keep all your important and frequently used items in the quick access front V dart gusseted pocket. With the mesh pockets on the side you don’t have to worry about lack of space for your water bottle or any other small items.

Apart from the above mentioned features the Wildcraft Eiger Rucksack-40 L has zippered mess pockets on the waist belt so that you can grasp necessary items without much worry. The sternum straps keep your shoulder straps in place and prevent them from shifting when you are on the move. You can clip on all your small items onto the D buckles on the shoulder pads. If you don’t want to strap on this bag onto your shoulders you can use the haul loop which facilitates easy portability. The reflective tape on this bag acts gives you visibility when it is dark. In order to enhance the durability and sturdiness this bag has been bar tacked on specialised machines. All your assets are kept secure with the buckle and zipper closure of this bag. This Wildcraft Eiger Rucksack-40 L keeps your load compact and organised.

  • 210 D Nylon Double Ripstop and 420 D Nylon Dobby

Relish all your adventurous activities with the Wildcraft Alpinist-55 L. This bag is sure to make your adventure trips more relaxing as well as amusing. Equipped with several useful features this bag makes packing unpacking and carrying the load around an easy job for you. This unisex and free size bag is apt for activities like camping hiking and trekking. This bag will give you a contented feeling of carrying the feeling. Designed to suit all weather conditions this smart bag promises to be by your side in varying situations. 

Body

Crafted from 210D Nylon Ripstop this Wildcraft rucksack will last you for a long time. Measuring 330.2 x 762 x 228.6 mm in dimension and weighing 2220 g this bag has a compact profile. The top loading facility of this bag allows you to organise your things in order of their use. You can backpack with this Wildcraft bag for several days as this bag has a carrying capacity of 55 litres. To alter the load according to your height and body this bag has shoulder weight and width adjusters provided on the shoulder pads. In order to keep all your belongings secure this bag has a zipper closure.

Features

The numerous features of the Wildcraft Alpinist-55 L make it difficult for any adventure buff to keep away from getting one. This bag has five pockets where you can accommodate all your items without increasing the size of the load. You can enjoy the snow without worrying about your belongings getting damp as the snow skirt feature of this bag prevents the snow from depositing in. When you don’t want to carry this bag around on your shoulders especially when the load is less you can use the reinforced haul loop. In order to make sure you reach your tools with ease when you need them in urgency this bag has walking stick and ice axe loops.   

While you are on the go to keep your load intact and prevent it from shifting around this Wildcraft rucksack has compression straps at the top and bottom. Giving a boost to your comfort this bag is equipped with a sleeping bag carrier on the hood and carry mat straps at the bottom so that you can snooze in comfort after the day’s activities. To ensure that your body doesn’t suffer at the end of your trips this bag has generously padded shoulders back and waist belt. Apart from this the Wildcraft rucksack has been designed with a detachable angular waist belt which acts as a weight distributor between the shoulders and the hip. The webbing on the waist belt is where you can clip on the carabiners when you want to do some hiking or mountaineering you could also hang small accessories too. You can modify the adjustable shoulder straps to match your convenience.

You can enjoy the natural showers without having to worry about possessions becoming moist as this bag comes with a zippered rain cover pocket at the base. The concealed zippered pocket on the hood is the right place to keep the items which you need frequently. To make sure you do not feel guilty about leaving out some of your essentials due to lack of place this bag has an internal flat pocket and side balloon pockets where you can fit in all that you want. The collapsible zippered compartment makes extra room for all your items especially when you need to pack for a few more days. Bar tacked on specialised machines; this bag promises resilience and durability. Thus the Wildcraft Alpinist-55 L can be your trustworthy confidante for all your planned and unplanned trips.

Make the most out of your vacation by going on an adventure trip with the Wildcraft Cauvery Rucksack-60 L. Designed for both men and women  this free size bag is sure to catch any adventure buff’s attention. Enjoy a walk in the green meadows or a hike to the hilltop without feeling the strain of carrying the load with this smart and well-equipped rucksack.

Body

Crafted from 210D Nylon Ripstop this bag is immune to damages like tearing and ripping. Measuring 304.8 x 812.8 x 254 mm in dimension and weighing 2180 g this Wildcraft Cauvery Rucksack-60 L has a compact profile allowing you to travel around in peace. With a carrying capacity of 60 litres this bag can accommodate majority of your essentials for a long trip. The shoulder weight and width adjusters on the shoulders pads and the torso adjuster assure that the weight of your load is evened out between your shoulders and hip along with putting less tension on your shoulders. The top loading style facilitates easy packing and unpacking.

Features

This Wildcraft Cauvery Rucksack-60 L allows you to enjoy the natural showers and at the same time keeps your belongings dry by protecting them with the zippered rain cover pocket at the base. In order to keep your load in place and prevent it from shifting this bag has compression straps at the top and bottom which give you the freedom to move around quickly and to participate in your favourite adventure activities with the least amount of hassle. To facilitate quick access to your tools in a situation where you need them the most this bag has walking stick and ice axe loops. Keeping your things dry and clean is the snow skirt which averts deposition of snow onto this Wildcraft rucksack. You can sleep in peace without having to carry extra luggage as this bag comes with a sleeping bag carrier on the hood. The reinforced haul loop can be used when the load is minimal and you don’t want to use the shoulder straps thus enabling easy portability. 

Equipped with five different pockets this bag will never give you an opportunity to complain about lack of space. To reach the items you need on the go you can place them in the concealed zippered pocket on the hood of this bag. The carry mat straps at the base make sure your comfort is never compromised on even in the most remote areas. Making space for your small items is the internal flat pocket where you can keep your last minute items and the detachable hood is another add-on which enables easy packing and unpacking. To distribute the weight between your hip and shoulders this bag has attached waist straps which can be fastened when the load is heavy these straps also keep your load in a fixed place especially when you need to jump climb or run. 

To add to your comfort this bag has generously padded shoulders back and waist belt this padding makes sure minimal amount of stress is put on your body. The webbing on the waist belt is the perfect place to clip on carabiners for trekking and hiking you can also clasp on some small accessories onto it. You can stop fretting about where to keep your soiled clothes and shoes as this bag has a special collapsible and zippered compartment for this. Boasting of capaciousness this bag has side air mesh pockets where you can keep the items you need in an emergency situation. The zipper closure of this bag keeps your possessions safe and secure and averts them from slipping off from your bag. Bar tacked on specialised machines this Wildcraft Cauvery Rucksack-60 L promises you durability and sturdiness.

Body

Made of 600 D Polyester and 450 D Polyester Ripstop this duffel bag is resilient to damages and at the same time durable. With dimensions measuring 711.2 x 279.4 x 279.4 mm and weighing 950 g this duffel bag is slender and at the same time lightweight thus making it easy for you to carry it around. As this bag measures 28 inches in size it is compact and can be carried easily on any mode of transportation.

This Wildcraft Duffel Bag has a carrying capacity of 56 litres which allows you to carry your clothes footwear and accessories in it comfortably. As this duffel bag is water-resistant it prevents your belongings from getting waterlogged when it rains. The detachable shoulder straps facilitate easy portability. Enabling you to carry this duffel bag comfortably are the color coordinated shoulder and handle straps.

Features

In the compartment of this Wildcraft Explorer 28 inch Duffel Bag – Unisex you can keep your clothes whereas the three pockets can be reserved for accessories gadgets and miscellaneous items. The wet pocket is where you can keep your wet clothes and belongings. You can slip in your dirty shoes or clothes into the collapsible compartment on the side. Your knick-knacks can be placed in the side pocket of this duffel bag. To enhance your comfort further this duffel bag has been provided with padded shoulder support.

Providing this Wildcraft Duffel Bag with stability when you place it on the ground are the heavy duty studs on the base which also reduce wear and tear. The mesh pocket on the side is where you can keep fragile items and gadgets. As this bag is bar tacked on specialised machines it is sure to last you for a long time. With the pull of a zip all your possessions will get safely encased within this duffel bag.

This Wildcraft Eiger Rucksack can be used by both men and women and comes with a capacity of 40 L. The rucksack is made of nylon which is known for its durability and long lasting nature. The material is also very light. The rucksack comes with a zipper closure that ensures that all your possessions remain secure. It also comes with two ice axe loops and a zippered mesh pocket on the waist belt as well.

The rucksack comes with a sleeve for a 16 in. laptop and four pockets as well. This rucksack from Wildcraft has a shoulder strap too which can be adjusted to suit your convenience. The rucksack also has back padding that ensures that it is comfortable to carry around as well.
